wiki.summary: “Lotus” is the second track on Lil Uzi Vert vs. the World 2, which also serves as the deluxe version of Lil Uzi Vert’s second studio album, Eternal Atake. The track was previewed in 2018 by Uzi on an Instagram live video on Young Thug’s Instagram account. On March 7, 2020, Uzi tweeted lyrics from the pre-chorus of “Lotus”: "I pull up in a lamb this not a lotussssssssss ….."
